The `.config/` directory is the root directory for configurations that work
with the [XDG Base Directory Specification][xdg].

Since this potentially encompasses a lot of configuration that I might not care
about, I'm gitignoring the entire tree `git add -f`'ing files when the time
comes.

[xdg]: https://specifications.freedesktop.org/basedir-spec/basedir-spec-latest.html
